{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/post/punya-pasangan-penggila-mainan-gak-masalah-tuh/","result":{"data":{"wordpressPost":{"title":"Punya Pasangan Penggila Mainan? Gak Masalah Tuh!","content":"<p>Saat ini, udah banyak banget cara untuk melepas stress, salah satunya dengan bermain. Kita bisa memilih untuk bermain <em>game online</em> atau mainan seperti robot-robotan. Tapi gimana jadinya kalau pacar atau pendamping hidup kamu punya hobi yang berlebihan sama mainan mereka? Uhh, bisa-bisa kita dinomor duakan deh!</p>\n<p>Eits, tapi jangan sebel dulu ya sama pasangan kamu. Meski terkadang bisa memberikan dampak positif maupun negatif, bisa jadi menyenangkan juga kok. Nggak melulu menyebalkan, memang sih selalu ada suka dan dukannya, tapi kamu harus berusaha memakluminya nih. Seperti komik <em>My Toy Geek Husband</em> yang ber-<em>genre slice of life </em>terbaru di <em>CIAYO Comics</em> nih. Penasaran kan lika-likunya kalau punya suami yang hobi ngoleksi mainan? Langsung aja nih baca komiknya ya!</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_45483\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-45483\" data-attachment-id=\"45483\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/punya-pasangan-penggila-mainan-gak-masalah-tuh/attachment/mtto5/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/mtto5.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Sumber: CIAYO Comics\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Sumber: CIAYO Comics&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/mtto5-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/mtto5.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-45483\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/mtto5.jpg\" alt=\"Sumber: CIAYO Comics\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/mtto5.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/mtto5-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-45483\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: CIAYO Comics</p></div></p>\n<p><em>My Toy Geek Husband</em> bercerita mengenai Fira yang punya suami bernama Andra dan hobi mengoleksi mainan berupa robot-robotan nih. Eits, selain menjadi ibu rumah tangga, ternyata Fira juga punya usaha sampingan yaitu online shop loh. Meskipun di rumah aja tapi bisa juga mempunyai penghasilan nih kayak Fira! Lumayan buat nambah uang belanja bulanan nih!</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_45480\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-45480\" data-attachment-id=\"45480\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/punya-pasangan-penggila-mainan-gak-masalah-tuh/attachment/mtto1/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/mtto1.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Sumber: CIAYO Comics\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Sumber: CIAYO Comics&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/mtto1-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/mtto1.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-45480\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/mtto1.jpg\" alt=\"Sumber: CIAYO Comics\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/mtto1.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/mtto1-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-45480\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: CIAYO Comics</p></div></p>\n<p>Nah, selain itu Fira mempunyai anak laki-laki bernama Tama yang berusia 6 tahun. Meski usianya masih terbilang kecil, tapi Tama ini juga suka nge-<em>vlog</em> loh a.k.a jadi youtuber cilik. Kira-kira apa aja sih yang jadi bahan Tama nge-<em>vlog</em>? Duh, kecil-kecil cabe rawit!</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_45479\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-45479\" data-attachment-id=\"45479\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/punya-pasangan-penggila-mainan-gak-masalah-tuh/attachment/m9/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/m9.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Sumber: CIAYO Comics\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Sumber: CIAYO Comics&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/m9-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/m9.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-45479\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/m9.jpg\" alt=\"Sumber: CIAYO Comics\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/m9.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/m9-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-45479\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: CIAYO Comics</p></div></p>\n<p>Buat kamu yang punya saudara, adik, atau anak ada baiknya kamu ikut mendukung kegiatan yang mereka minati, kayak Fira nih yang selalu siap jadi kameramen dadakan anaknya. Ihh, gemas ya sama Fira dan anaknya!</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_45481\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-45481\" data-attachment-id=\"45481\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/punya-pasangan-penggila-mainan-gak-masalah-tuh/attachment/mtto3/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/mtto3.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Sumber: CIAYO Comics\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Sumber: CIAYO Comics&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/mtto3-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/mtto3.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-45481\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/mtto3.jpg\" alt=\"Sumber: CIAYO Comics\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/mtto3.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/mtto3-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-45481\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: CIAYO Comics</p></div></p>\n<p>Wah, kali ini Tama mau buat video <em>youtube</em> yang kekinian yaitu <em>unboxing</em>. Eh, tapi yang di <em>unboxing </em>malah mainan papinya nih. Kira-kira gimana ya respon Andra saat liat video <em>unboxing</em> anaknya ini? Hehe, harus ijin nih Tama lain kali ke papinya.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_45482\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-45482\" data-attachment-id=\"45482\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/punya-pasangan-penggila-mainan-gak-masalah-tuh/attachment/mtto4/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/mtto4.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Sumber: CIAYO Comics\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Sumber: CIAYO Comics&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/mtto4-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/mtto4.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-45482\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/mtto4.jpg\" alt=\"Sumber: CIAYO Comics\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/mtto4.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/mtto4-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-45482\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: CIAYO Comics</p></div></p>\n<p>Waduh, kepala robotnya sampai lepas nih! Siap-siap Andra jantungan deh, robot kesayangannya jadi bahan percobaan anaknya nih. Kalau mainan kamu sampai rusak, gimana ya perasaanmu?</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_45483\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-45483\" data-attachment-id=\"45483\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/punya-pasangan-penggila-mainan-gak-masalah-tuh/attachment/mtto5/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/mtto5.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Sumber: CIAYO Comics\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Sumber: CIAYO Comics&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/mtto5-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/mtto5.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-45483\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/mtto5.jpg\" alt=\"Sumber: CIAYO Comics\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/mtto5.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/mtto5-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-45483\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: CIAYO Comics</p></div></p>\n<p>Kalau kamu mengemari sesuatu pasti akan ada satu hari yang kamu gunakan untuk memenuhi hasrat akan hobimu itu, benar nggak? Nah, itu juga yang terjadi ke Andra, saat dia sedang pergi menghabiskan waktu dengan teman dan hobinya, tau-tau Fira menelepon nih. Hayo, jangan bohong ya karena ternyata pasangan kamu udah hafal nih sama jadwalmu!</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_45484\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-45484\" data-attachment-id=\"45484\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/punya-pasangan-penggila-mainan-gak-masalah-tuh/attachment/mtto6/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/mtto6.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Sumber: CIAYO Comics\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Sumber: CIAYO Comics&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/mtto6-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/mtto6.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-45484\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/mtto6.jpg\" alt=\"Sumber: CIAYO Comics\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/mtto6.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/mtto6-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-45484\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: CIAYO Comics</p></div></p>\n<p>Duh, suka susah ya kalau nemenin pasangan ngobrol sama teman-temannya, apalagi kalau yang dibahas itu hal-hal yang kamu nggak paham.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_45485\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-45485\" data-attachment-id=\"45485\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/punya-pasangan-penggila-mainan-gak-masalah-tuh/attachment/mtto7/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/mtto7.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Sumber: CIAYO Comics\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Sumber: CIAYO Comics&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/mtto7-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/mtto7.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-45485\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/mtto7.jpg\" alt=\"Sumber: CIAYO Comics\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/mtto7.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/mtto7-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-45485\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: CIAYO Comics</p></div></p>\n<p>Tuh, Fira aja sampai bingung suaminya ngomong apaan. Berasa lagi dengar bahasa dari planet lainnya. Kira-kira di kamus apa ya yang bisa nerjemahinnya?</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_45486\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-45486\" data-attachment-id=\"45486\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/punya-pasangan-penggila-mainan-gak-masalah-tuh/attachment/mtto8/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/mtto8.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Sumber: CIAYO Comics\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Sumber: CIAYO Comics&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/mtto8-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/mtto8.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-45486\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/mtto8.jpg\" alt=\"Sumber: CIAYO Comics\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/mtto8.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/mtto8-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-45486\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: CIAYO Comics</p></div></p>\n<p>Tapi, yang namanya sayang mah selalu menerima apapun kekurangan pasanganmu, yang terpenting bisa menghabiskan waktu bersama aja udah cukup nih. Kayak Fira dan Andra yang menghabiskan waktu bersama meski diruangan yang penuh dengan mainan. Nggak apa-apa deh sempit-sempitan, yang penting tetap berduaan. Duh<em>, so sweet</em>-nya!</p>\n<p>Buat kamu yang mau tau kelanjutan lika-liku Fira dan Andra, jangan lewatin update-an setiap episode-nya hanya di <em>CIAYO Comics</em> ya! Kalau kamu punya ide yang nggak kalah menarik dari komik <em>My Toy Geek Husband</em>, langsung aja ikutan <em>CIAYO Comic Challenge Vol. 3</em> dan menangin beragam hadiahnya.</p>\n"}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"id":"781cef49-2947-52e3-96a6-958b138d9c4a"}}}